Lucia: Is this anglerfish also yours?

1572
00:56:14,733 --> 00:56:17,800
Jake:走走走哈哈哈
Jake: Let's go, let's go, hahaha.

1573
00:56:18,233 --> 00:56:20,333
Shure: 这是我我们老的队名
Shure: This was our old team name.

1574
00:56:27,966 --> 00:56:28,766
Tasha: 这个
Tasha: This one.

1575
00:56:30,333 --> 00:56:32,300
Tasha: 就可以让这个蛋挞爆浆
Tasha: This can make the egg tart burst with filling.

1576
00:56:37,333 --> 00:56:38,700
Tasha: 你把它搁进去
Tasha: You put it in.

1577
00:56:39,900 --> 00:56:42,833
其他人：加糖吗那种焦糖是怎么做的
Others: Do you add sugar? How do you make caramel?

1578
00:56:43,566 --> 00:56:44,566
Tasha: 焦糖吗
Tasha: Caramel?

1579
00:56:44,933 --> 00:56:47,500
Tasha: 焦糖的话就是在表面的话会用
Tasha: For caramel, you'd use it on the surface.

1580
00:56:47,966 --> 00:56:49,300
Tasha: 再再用高火
Tasha: Then use high heat.

1581
00:56:49,400 --> 00:56:50,733
其他人：这可以直接吃吗
Others: Can we eat this directly?

1582
00:56:50,700 --> 00:56:51,500
Tasha: 可以
Tasha: Yes.

1583
00:56:57,933 --> 00:56:59,266
其他人：这有点甜算了
Others: This is a bit sweet, forget it.

1584
00:57:03,300 --> 00:57:05,900
其他人：焦糖这有点像代可可脂
Others: This caramel is kind of like cocoa butter substitute.

1585
00:57:04,700 --> 00:57:05,500
Tasha: 黑壳
Tasha: Dark shell.

1586
00:57:05,966 --> 00:57:06,666
Tasha: 不是代可可脂
Tasha: Not cocoa butter substitute.

1587
00:57:06,666 --> 00:57:07,966
Tasha: 纯可可脂
Tasha: Pure cocoa butter.

1588
00:57:13,600 --> 00:57:14,566
其他人：你看啊
Others: Look at this.

1589
00:57:17,400 --> 00:57:18,800
其他人：反而不是那种巧克力
Others: It's not that kind of chocolate.

1590
00:57:25,533 --> 00:57:26,566
其他人：这就一个鸡蛋
Others: It's just one egg.

1591
00:57:26,566 --> 00:57:27,466
其他人：还占了壳
Others: And it's taking up the shell.

1592
00:57:33,600 --> 00:57:35,833
其他人：这个声是提前明白的
Others: This sound is understood in advance.

1593
00:57:37,433 --> 00:57:38,233
Tasha: 绅士鸡蛋
Tasha: Gentleman's egg.

1594
00:57:42,233 --> 00:57:43,133
Tasha: 没削好
Tasha: Didn't peel it well.

1595
00:57:46,866 --> 00:57:48,300
Tasha: 也都可以直接吃
Tasha: You can eat it directly too.

1596
00:57:56,866 --> 00:57:58,733
Tasha: 最终大家一起去取快递了
Tasha: In the end, everyone went to pick up the package together.

1597
00:57:59,100 --> 00:58:00,200
其他人：好像是
Others: Seems like it.

1598
00:58:43,233 --> 00:58:44,133
其他人：为啥加巧克力
Others: Why add chocolate?

1599
00:58:44,133 --> 00:58:46,100
其他人：它会爆浆
Others: It will burst with filling.

1600
00:58:47,700 --> 00:58:49,666
其他人：哦你说它回头会爆浆
Others: Oh, you mean it will burst with filling later.

1601
00:58:49,866 --> 00:58:51,900
Tasha: 嗯对
Tasha: Yeah, right.

1602
00:58:50,033 --> 00:58:52,000
其他人：咬的时候会爆浆
Others: It will burst when you bite it.

1603
00:58:52,233 --> 00:58:53,733
其他人：那就那个熔岩什么的
Others: Like that lava thing.

1604
00:58:54,066 --> 00:58:55,033
Tasha: 嗯对
Tasha: Yeah, right.

1605
00:58:56,400 --> 00:58:57,066
其他人：那他们有
Others: They have it.

1606
00:58:57,066 --> 00:59:02,000
其他人：比如熔岩草莓是什么固态的草莓酱
Others: Like lava strawberry, which is solid strawberry jam.

1607
00:59:01,333 --> 00:59:02,133
Tasha: 什么
Tasha: What?

1608
00:59:02,366 --> 00:59:03,300
其他人：熔岩草莓
Others: Lava strawberry.

1609
00:59:04,533 --> 00:59:07,733
Tasha: 没吃过熔岩草莓就是
Tasha: Never had lava strawberry.

1610
00:59:09,400 --> 00:59:10,333
其他人：能不能做几个不带这个
Others: Can we make some without it?

1611
00:59:12,266 --> 00:59:12,933
Tasha: 那就第一排
Tasha: Then the first row.

1612
00:59:12,933 --> 00:59:13,266
其他人：好
Others: Okay.

1613
00:59:12,933 --> 00:59:15,333
Tasha: 不带你你匀过去吧
Tasha: Without it, you distribute them.

1614
00:59:26,066 --> 00:59:26,966
其他人：多加几个
Others: Add a few more.

1615
00:59:35,500 --> 00:59:36,333
Tasha: 好了吗
Tasha: Done yet?

1616
00:59:37,300 --> 00:59:38,500
Tasha: 这个好多呀
Tasha: This is a lot.

1617
00:59:39,066 --> 00:59:40,900
其他人：   就是要来几个特别多的
Others: Just need a few with a lot.

1618
00:59:43,800 --> 00:59:45,200
其他人：我到了
Others: I'm here.

1619
00:59:44,500 --> 00:59:45,166
Tasha: 行你倒吧
Tasha: Alright, you pour it.

1620
00:59:45,166 --> 00:59:46,433
Tasha: 倒个8分满就行
Tasha: Just fill it 80%.

1621
00:59:46,933 --> 00:59:47,933
Tasha: 哎你没关系
Tasha: Hey, no worries.

1622
00:59:47,933 --> 00:59:49,833
Tasha: 你就把倒满12个就行
Tasha: Just fill up twelve evenly.

1623
00:59:49,833 --> 00:59:51,066
Tasha: 均匀一点即可
Tasha: Just make it even.

